He misses the threat and gets bolshy....

Now he sees it and resigns. k-h7 draws Rxg7, forced then with Qxg7 and QxQ mate. I managed to gain quite an advantage beforehand but I do like the closing sequence. I'm usually bad at linking pieces together in an attack, its usually one piece charges, gets killed, second piece charges and so on.... so to have a combi like this was most satisfying. To me at any rate.
